Package org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.server

Interface HTTPOauth2AuthorizationMechanismCfg

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Configuration, HTTPAuthorizationMechanismCfg
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HTTPOauth2CtsAuthorizationMechanismCfg, HTTPOauth2FileAuthorizationMechanismCfg, HTTPOauth2OpenamAuthorizationMechanismCfg, HTTPOauth2TokenIntrospectionAuthorizationMechanismCfg
    public interface HTTPOauth2AuthorizationMechanismCfg
extends HTTPAuthorizationMechanismCfg
    A server-side interface for querying HTTP Oauth2 Authorization Mechanism settings.

    The HTTP Oauth2 Authorization Mechanism is used to define HTTP OAuth2 authorization mechanism.
